{"tid":1259183,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「長期戰」大家有冇諗過 - 北向文宣戰法？","createTime":"2019-06-26T13:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T00:19:09.000Z","uid":5086,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3ebe94d0cc0af6f4f502bb3742bb6e223afb79","tid":1259183,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"係呢次運動入面<br />\n已經見到我地嘅文宣力量係幾咁勁<br />\n好多自己發起嘅播片 派傳單等等<br />\n不過我地主要嘅對象都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇諗過 如果我地長遠要贏呢場仗<br />\n我地要改變嘅 唔係淨係呢個香港木偶政府<br />\n而係要中共呢個政權動搖 甚至結束一黨專政<br />\n<br />\n而大陸人要接觸民主思想<br />\n透過網絡 其實好難<br />\n既然係咁 我地長遠係咪可以係香港嘅旅遊區<br />\n做一啲文宣去宣揚民主思想<br />\n講多啲六四呀 好多不公義嘅維權問題等等<br />\n去影響佢地 以致民主思潮可以慢慢滲透去中國<br />\n等中國都可以有佢地嘅雨傘運動 享受到民主自由呢？<br />\n<br />\n等到真係有逃犯條例<br />\n就唔會再有機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得長遠有冇得諗？反正唔犯法"},{"pid":"aa627cf9fc50bd2107764cc564fe7eebc222aef5","tid":1259183,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"推 係咪開錯左台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab813eb6f568970895fe07791aa0f6f54040e3df","tid":1259183,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65844f30eab2a816ebc70fb3f4c41fd6a4c44bfd","tid":1259183,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aa4ae7dee4663f06caf06845105d97db7c078a6","tid":1259183,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f40d1faad25146d84985a034184e330a4414d17c","tid":1259183,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15b546ddc6f77d6fa6c45a2aec69a0da6603a1f0","tid":1259183,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,